OL,3,CRemembering the Boxing Day floods 10
OL,4,Cyears on
OL,6,FReport by Granada Reports' journalist,
OL,7,FEmma Sweeney
OL,9,FIt was Boxing Day 2015 and, while many
OL,10,Fwere still enjoying the festivities,
OL,11,Fparts of the UK were hit by what was
OL,12,Fdescribed at the time as the worst
OL,13,Fflooding in a generation.
OL,15,FAfter weeks of heavy rain brought by
OL,16,FStorm Desmond, Storm Eva swept in,
OL,17,Fdumping intense rainfall on already
OL,18,Fsaturated ground and triggering some
OL,19,Fof the most severe flooding the UK had
OL,20,Fseen in decades.
