OL,3,CRemembering the Boxing Day floods 10
OL,4,Cyears on
OL,6,FThe River Irwell and the River Roch in
OL,7,FGreater Manchester burst their banks,
OL,8,Foverwhelming defences.
OL,10,FHundreds of properties and businesses
OL,11,Fwere affected in Salford, Rochdale and
OL,12,FBury.
OL,14,FMohammad Sheraz was one of several
OL,15,Fvolunteers in Rochdale who still
OL,16,Fremembers the scale of the response
OL,17,Ften years on.
OL,19,F"People were coming throughout the day
OL,20,Fdropping off sandbags after an urgent
OL,21,Fappeal went out," he said.
