OL,3,CRemembering the Boxing Day floods 10
OL,4,Cyears on
OL,6,F"They brought blankets, tinned food
OL,7,Fand cereal ` essentials we needed for
OL,8,Fthe days ahead ` because people had
OL,9,Flost everything, or weren't allowed
OL,10,Fback into their homes."
OL,12,FIn the aftermath of the floods a multi-
OL,13,Fmillion pound scheme ` which includes
OL,14,Fthe construction of a flood storage
OL,15,Freservoir and sections of flood
OL,16,Fdefences along the River Roch ` was
OL,17,Fannounced.
OL,19,FThe defences have been designed to
OL,20,Fprotect 723 homes and 489 businesses
OL,21,Fin Rochdale and Littleborough.
