OL,6,FWhile work is still ongoing the
OL,7,Fcouncil says protections have already
OL,8,Fbeen strengthened.
OL,10,FDeputy Leader of Rochdale Council
OL,11,FTricia Ayrton said: "I'm very
OL,12,Fconfident we won't see flooding like
OL,13,Fthat again in Rochdale".
OL,15,FShe added: "We've put infrastructure
OL,16,Fin place so there's less water coming
OL,17,Fdown into the town and off the moors.
OL,26,@sD@UOUuD@WO]wD@LOU
