OL,3,CRemembering the Boxing Day floods 10
OL,4,Cyears on
OL,6,FProfessor Tom Coulthard from
OL,7,FManchester Metropolitan University
OL,8,Fsaid: "I think you can spend money on
OL,9,Fincreasing flood defences in certain
OL,10,Fareas up to a point, but ultimately we
OL,11,Fhave to recognise that we need to live
OL,12,Fwith flooding to a degree and accept
OL,13,Fthat it might well happen at some time
OL,14,Fand maybe make our houses and our
OL,15,Flives a bit more resilient to that
OL,16,Frisk.
OL,18,F"Quite simply, with climate change, if
OL,19,Fyou have a warmer world, the
OL,20,Fatmosphere can hold more water", he
OL,21,Fadded.
